<p><i><b>Pay It Forward</b></i> is a <a href="/wiki/2000_in_film" title="2000 in film">2000</a> <a href="/wiki/Cinema_of_the_United_States" title="Cinema of the United States">American</a> <a href="/wiki/Drama_film" title="Drama film">dramatic</a> <a href="/wiki/Film" title="Film">film</a> based on the novel of the same name by <a href="/wiki/Catherine_Ryan_Hyde" title="Catherine Ryan Hyde">Catherine Ryan Hyde</a>.</p>
